%% Fluxo Crítico: Memory Extraction e Recall
%% Referência: docs/blueprint/07-critical_flows.md

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Agent as Agent
    participant MemMgr as MemoryManager
    participant LLM as OpenRouterClient
    participant Store as SQLiteMemoryStore
    participant Embed as EmbeddingService
    participant DB as SQLiteDatabase

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Agent, DB: EXTRAÇÃO (após cada turno)

        Agent ->> MemMgr: shouldExtract(messages)
        MemMgr ->> MemMgr: avaliar triggers (explícito, turnos>10, sampling 30%)

        alt trigger ativado
            MemMgr ->>+ LLM: chat(extractionPrompt, lastMessages)
            LLM -->>- MemMgr: fatos estruturados [{content, category, scope}]

            loop para cada fato extraído
                MemMgr ->> Store: save(memory)
                Store ->>+ Embed: embed([content])
                Embed ->> Embed: verificar cache LRU

                alt cache miss
                    Embed ->>+ LLM: embed(texts)
                    LLM -->>- Embed: number[][]
                end

                Embed -->>- Store: embedding
                Store ->> DB: INSERT INTO memories + UPDATE memories_fts
            end

            MemMgr -->> Agent: emit(memory_extracted)
        else trigger não ativado
            MemMgr -->> Agent: skip
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Agent, DB: RECALL (durante ContextPipeline)

        Agent ->> MemMgr: recall(query)
        MemMgr ->> Store: search(query, limit)

        par Busca Híbrida
            Store ->> DB: SELECT FROM memories_fts MATCH query
            Note right of DB: FTS5 full-text (sem API cost)
        and
            Store ->>+ Embed: embed([query])
            Embed -->>- Store: queryEmbedding
            Store ->> Store: cosine similarity vs todos embeddings
            Note right of Store: Brute-force OK para ≤100K
        end

        Store ->> Store: Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF)
        Store ->> Store: ponderar por confidence
        Store ->> DB: UPDATE access_count, confidence (+0.05)
        Store -->> MemMgr: Memory[] rankeadas
        MemMgr -->> Agent: Memory[] para injeção no contexto
    end
